triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunSettings.attributes.description.particleType=The type of particles that indicate the bullet trajectory.\nFire and Ice have a third color (red/cyan). A new field will appear if you chose the Custom type.
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunSettings.attributes.description.customParticleTexture=The path to your particle texture is the Type chosen is Custom.\nRelative to Atlases/Gameplay/.
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunSettings.attributes.description.directions=Whether the player should be able to shoot cardinally, cardinally+diagonally, or only left and right.
