triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunSettings.attributes.description.canShootInFeather=Whether the player should have the gun available while in the feather state.
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunSettings.attributes.description.freezeFrames=How many freeze frames should give each shot.
