triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunInteractions.attributes.description.collectTouchSwitches=Whether bullets should be able to collect touch switches (vanilla or Flag Touch Switches from Helping Hand).
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunInteractions.attributes.description.collectBadelineOrbs=Whether bullets should make badeline orbs to absorb the player upon contact.
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunInteractions.attributes.description.useFeathers=Whether bullets should be able to use feathers (or permanently destroy their bubbles if shielded).
triggers.KoseiHelper/NemesisGunInteractions.attributes.description.coreModeToggles=Whether bullets should be able to swap Core Mode Toggles.
